Simple script to generate an HTML presentation having
audio synched with contents.

Inspired from <http://www.toolness.com/wp/2010/02/herdict-firefox-integration-and-better-html-presentations/>

USAGE
-----

Call the script from command line passing as argument a configuration
file using the YAML format

 $ python generate_presentation.py config.yaml > presentation.html

e load the created page in the browser.
